            "stanza_text": "Ainsi, les nuits dans les tranchées,\nL'arme au pied, le froid et la faim,\nLes dures souffrances cachées\nD'une attente morne et sans fin ;"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 2,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 5,
                    "line_text": "Les batailles, les escarmouches,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 6,
                    "line_text": "Le sang qui coule sur vos pas,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 7,
                    "line_text": "Et les fusillades farouches",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
